      "role": "user",
      "content": "I hear you, but I'm trying to understand the logic of the skeptics so I don't look biased in the meeting. If someone were to argue that the \"catastrophic\" scenarios you're mentioning are actually just science fiction being used to justify heavy-handed government intervention that could destroy innovation, how would they frame that? Is there any merit to the idea that the actual danger is the regulation itself slowing down helpful progress?",
